For Grandmother Eid Mubarak Lanterns Moon Stars Card

Review For Grandmother Eid Mubarak Lanterns Moon Stars Card – Eid Cards This item is trending! For Grandmother Eid Mubarak Lanterns Moon Stars Card It’s a great choice For Grandmother Eid Mubarak Lanterns Moon Stars Card See more about itA stylish greeting card for your grandmother, with decorative lettering outline in gold-effect and filled with brightly coloured islamic patterns. The front cover greeting is, ‘Eid Mubarak. to my dear Grandmother’ There is a brightly coloured lantern in the bottom left corner, hanging underneath the letter ‘E’ and a patterned moon and star in the top right hand corner, with two more lanterns and an Islamic Star suspended from the moon. The white background on the front cover is lightly textured and the inside message is just a suggestion which you can easily change or delete if you wish. Price:$4.42
